title: Bloomberg Markets: Snap Slips Below IPO Price Amid Doubts
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Snap Slips Below IPO Price Amid Doubts
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Alex Barinka IPO Reporter Bloomberg News Discussing Snap Inc. shares falling below their initial public offering price for the first time amid questions about the company’s ability to grow as fast as initially expected and after recent declines in technology stocks worldwide.
